org.apache.paimon.flink.sink

Interface Committer<CommitT,GlobalCommitT>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StoreCommitter, StoreMultiCommitter

    public interface Committer<CommitT,GlobalCommitT>
extends AutoCloseable
    The Committer is responsible for creating and committing an aggregated committable, which we call committable (see combine(long, long, java.util.List<CommitT>)).

    The Committer runs with parallelism equal to 1.
